{"tid":2147279,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"撕走「生物危害」標貼  中龍口水樣本送工廈 化驗廢物棄後梯","createTime":"2020-08-09T06:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T06:59:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"05dc68a31adb45fbbcb118fedb8e6a9b226e860e","tid":2147279,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:41:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200809/2LEDHDEYSYOBDDZ4Q7VEQJRI6A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2F2LEDHDEYSYOBDDZ4Q7VEQJRI6A%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminIlS5wRbVpD6X1tjwtO29R8%3D&h=4ed8e2bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2F2LEDHDEYSYOBDDZ4Q7VEQJRI6A%2F&h=4b0c15ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200809/2LEDHDEYSYOBDDZ4Q7VEQJRI6A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n撕走「生物危害」標貼 <br />\n中龍口水樣本送工廈 化驗廢物棄後梯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【武肺再爆發】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎第三波疫情大爆發下慈雲山淪為疫區，早前港府「欽點」為首批慈雲山居民提供檢測的中龍檢驗認證（香港）有限公司，因無經營醫務化驗業務資格，須交由其他醫務化驗所化驗。《蘋果》追查發現，中龍其中一所夥拍的化驗所位於荔枝角工廈，兩者董事關係千絲萬縷，但該化驗所不在16間政府認可武肺檢測機構名單內，亦未獲相關認可資格，更涉嫌隨意棄置檢測醫療廢物，恐增加播毒風險。<br />\n<br />\n記者：馮智敏 盧藹雯<br />\n<br />\n政府早前繞過公開招標直接向三間化驗所採購，國企中國檢驗有限公司子公司中龍為其中一間，負責為首批約四萬名慈雲山居民做深喉唾液樣本檢測；惟第二期慈雲山檢測計劃與政府最新公佈的全民檢測計劃承辦商不包括中龍。按照創新科技署轄下的香港實驗所認可計劃，中龍獲得非醫務化驗所和校正實驗所認可，可檢測玩具、化妝品、食物容器等，但不符合「醫務化驗所──質量及能力要求」的ISO 15189認證，故不能進行病毒樣本測試，須夥拍其他合資格化驗所進行。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ACjDg4yquXoWT3QyaPF16FJEYOM=/1309x1135/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4GHANJM7SISGF62J7RSHD553PI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FACjDg4yquXoWT3QyaPF16FJEYOM%3D%2F1309x1135%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4GHANJM7SISGF62J7RSHD553PI.gif&h=65c5d820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n直擊中龍亂棄化驗廢物<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：化驗師與外判關係複雜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jJMlC7syLPnRP8684l0lo2Sil5M=/647x431/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5R6GED3CYRCHW53OJX643XC6V4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjJMlC7syLPnRP8684l0lo2Sil5M%3D%2F647x431%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5R6GED3CYRCHW53OJX643XC6V4.gif&h=90af0be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【工人接走】沒穿保護衣的物流工人到慈樂邨取走口水樣本，未回應樣本去向。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/xesQhkIVa_ACgTliQb1CIjhEL_M=/647x431/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VREQ5S4VRHTU6VSTSPVUBV2VO4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FxesQhkIVa_ACgTliQb1CIjhEL_M%3D%2F647x431%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVREQ5S4VRHTU6VSTSPVUBV2VO4.gif&h=ffdc50fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【標貼失蹤】工人將逾10袋樣本送到荔枝角時豐中心的化驗所，袋上「生物危害」標貼不翼而飛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_QLmSdxF2bCnwp4DQ_YD80WS4Wk=/647x431/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GNADN6WLO3AZAND6O7IOM7S5BQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_QLmSdxF2bCnwp4DQ_YD80WS4Wk%3D%2F647x431%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGNADN6WLO3AZAND6O7IOM7S5BQ.gif&h=2da22f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【後梯播毒】貼有「生物危害」的黑色大膠袋遭棄置在化驗所樓層後樓梯，恐有播毒風險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2o1zwXGrEsI6LgtxxpI8o_Tuayk=/647x431/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IAUVKSOOGY7U4TIYIPDRE2ORSM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2o1zwXGrEsI6LgtxxpI8o_Tuayk%3D%2F647x431%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIAUVKSOOGY7U4TIYIPDRE2ORSM.gif&h=f07ea909&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【內有乾坤】膠袋裝滿收集樣本瓶的透明密實袋，混雜用過的紙巾及採樣須知等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n醫生：應放紅膠袋焚化<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。，物流工人其後到場收走樣本送上貨車運走，工人全程無穿保護衣物。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。之前黑色膠袋上的生物危害標誌不翼而飛，只剩寫有樣本來自大廈的便條紙。<br />\n<br />\n有清潔工指，近一星期在上址的梯間清理大批醫療廢物，擔心受感染。記者在同層後樓梯發現五個黑色膠袋，疑是該化驗所棄置的醫療廢物，當中一個貼有生物危害標誌，另一個貼上寫着「慈雲山 民裕」的便利貼，相信是收集樣本瓶的同一黑膠袋。黑膠袋內雖不見樣本瓶，但內裏裝滿收集樣本瓶的透明密實袋，使用過的紙巾、收集深喉唾液樣本須知等，令人擔心處理不當會有播毒風險。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。任職醫生的立法會議員郭家麒表示，直接接觸到樣本瓶的塑膠袋應當作醫療廢物處理，而非隨便棄置於工廈後樓梯。"},{"pid":"7cc10ff7341b95685ded4147e73653fcf32628ad","tid":2147279,"uid":200663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:43:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cda150c380d98d02ebb58fbcbe8bad523e3a368","tid":2147279,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff92f7014d21a2125bbc1cd658392cf00825738c","tid":2147279,"uid":233325,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:46:57.000Z","msg":"放入紅膠袋燒要錢，佢地想拎錢走，理L得你香港人同個環境"},{"pid":"cc9dbe5bb941ae4c9412e49fce0638b7a9756dd3","tid":2147279,"uid":133033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:48:00.000Z","msg":"呢啲就係支那既標準 佢哋既國內咁做係無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2733bf107f5fd11f3bb90b73b5555ae6da1e2b36","tid":2147279,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"005a15fd0d96861608a7286a592d241f1af9897d","tid":21