ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"DNA 送中，方艙集中營，屌你老母，香港人做錯啲乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c15b04206ca15f42a0be348d0f443d08e8e6c4","tid":2147279,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"終國標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"630951190e9ce3f9880fdbe7203394521fc01a7b","tid":2147279,"uid":137078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:55:39.000Z","msg":"Biohazards要放紅色膠袋<br />\nGeneral waste 黑色膠袋<br />\n啲垃圾唔係就咁抌去垃圾房<br />\n要有牌waste disposal公司收<br />\n不過洗乜跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e3ed132f165edb286725b6e5cda04bf18cd8a1","tid":2147279,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"正常好似要放落紅色膠袋，然後打嗰鵝頸結，再加上日期、邊間機構等等"},{"pid":"69cc97bf9f35dcbd05062741e936bf7864374710","tid":2147279,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"005a15fd0d96861608a7286a592d241f1af9897d","tid":2147279,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:49:01.000Z","msg":"條友手套都唔戴就掂咁勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:57:25.000Z","msg":"康復者嚟，自己有抗體話撚知你地死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158faf688ec05568d2d97badf933aba11b82572e","tid":2147279,"uid":149278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T06:59:42.000Z","msg":"推"}]}